            <div corresp="#c1190f2">
                <head>San Luis Potosi, Mexico.</head>
                <p>Walter F. Boyle, Consul, Cl. 5, lately assigned to Mexicali detailed to San Luis
                    Potosi as Consul in charge Feb. 7, 1922; assumed charge April 18, 1922. Assigned
                    to San Luis Potosi Oct. 2, 1923.</p>
                <p>David J. D. Myers, Consul, Cl. 4, lately assigned to Montevideo, was detailed,
                    temporarily to San Luis Potosi Aug. 30, 1922. Assigned to Durango Sept. 21,
                    1923.</p>
            </div>
